He keeps one launcher at his side for warning. He than arrested 
Choran and Imprisoner.

"You are charged with the murder of countless Maximal bots. You will 
remain in the Cybertronian Fire's brig until a proper trial is set. 
Please walk back peacefully with us to the Maximal base."
